NAME
    Sah::Schemas::DataSizeSpeed - Sah schemas related to data sizes & speeds
    (filesize, transfer speed, etc)

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.009 of Sah::Schemas::DataSizeSpeed
    (from Perl distribution Sah-Schemas-DataSizeSpeed), released on
    2020-03-08.

SAH SCHEMAS
    *   bandwidth

        Data transfer speed.

    *   dataquota

        Data transfer quota.

    *   datasize

        Data size.

        Float, in bytes.

        Can be coerced from string that contains units, e.g.:

         2KB   -> 2048      (kilobyte, 1024-based)
         2mb   -> 2097152   (megabyte, 1024-based)
         1.5K  -> 1536      (kilobyte, 1024-based)
         1.6ki -> 1600      (kibibyte, 1000-based)

    *   dataspeed

        Data transfer speed.

        Float, in bytes/second.

        Can be coerced from string that contains units, e.g.:

         1000kbps -> 128000 (kilobits per second, 1024-based)
         2.5 mbit -> 327680 (megabit per second, 1024-based)
         128KB/s  -> 131072 (kilobyte per second, 1024-based)

    *   filesize

        File size.

